<leg xml:space="preserve" billnum="HB0263" sponsor="Tyler Clancy" designation="HB" otherSponsor="Kirk A. Cullimore" otherHouse="Senate" subNumber="01" subSponsor="Kirk A. Cullimore" sess="2026GS" fileno="2026FL0625" date="2/20/2026 17:02:70" printDate="02-20 17:34" subVer="1" minVer="0" office="LEGISLATIVE GENERAL COUNSEL" actionDate="" impact="code"><info><nextbuid>33</nextbuid><aminfo anum="0" effdate="05/06/2026"><seclist><sect action="E" src="code" buid="7" uid="C41-1a-S1226_2026050620260506" sort="41 01a12260020260506" mtype="section" effdate="05/06/2026">41-1a-1226</sect><sect src="uncod" untype="effdate" buid="32" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" mtype="uncod" effdate="05/06/2026"/></seclist></aminfo></info><tbox><sinfo><nextpairid>0</nextpairid></sinfo><st numlevel="1" lineno="1" slineno="0-1">Heavy Duty Vehicle Amendments</st><sessionhead>2026 GENERAL SESSION</sessionhead><statehead>STATE OF UTAH</statehead><sponsorhead>Chief Sponsor: Tyler Clancy</sponsorhead><otherSponsorhead>Senate Sponsor: Kirk A. Cullimore</otherSponsorhead></tbox><lt numlevel="1" lineno="2" slineno="0-2"><lthead lineno="3">LONG TITLE</lthead><gdhead lineno="4">General Description:</gdhead><gd numlevel="1" lineno="5" slineno="0-5">This bill addresses provisions related to heavy duty vehicles.</gd><hphead lineno="6">Highlighted Provisions:</hphead><hp numlevel="1" lineno="7" slineno="0-7">This bill:<hl numlevel="1" lineno="8" slineno="0-8" level="1">defines terms;</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="9" slineno="0-9" level="1">establishes a heavy duty emissions compliance fee for a registration or renewal of a heavy <ln numlevel="1" lineno="10" slineno="0-10"/>duty vehicle with a 2009 or older model year;</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="11" slineno="0-11" level="1">provides for the deposit of revenue from the heavy duty emissions compliance fee into the <ln numlevel="1" lineno="12" slineno="0-12"/>Transportation Fund; and</hl><hl numlevel="1" lineno="13" slineno="0-13" level="1">makes technical and conforming changes.</hl></hp><moni numlevel="1" lineno="14" slineno="0-14" display="none">Money Appropriated in this Bill:</moni><moniNone lineno="15">None</moniNone><oc numlevel="1" lineno="16" slineno="0-16">Other Special Clauses:</oc><ocNone lineno="17">None</ocNone><sa numlevel="1" lineno="18" slineno="0-18">Utah Code Sections Affected:<saent numlevel="1" lineno="19" slineno="0-19"><snhead>ENACTS:</snhead><sn num="41-1a-1226" src="code" uid="C41-1a-S1226_2026050620260506" buid="7" sort="41 01a12260020260506" numlevel="1" lineno="20" slineno="0-20"><bold>41-1a-1226</bold>, Utah Code Annotated 1953</sn></saent></sa></lt><enacthead lineno="21"/><enact numlevel="1" lineno="22" slineno="0-22">Be it enacted by the Legislature of the state of Utah:</enact><bdy><bsec buid="7" num="41-1a-1226" type="enact" src="code" uid="C41-1a-S1226_2026050620260506" sort="41 01a12260020260506" numlevel="1" lineno="23" slineno="1-1" sn="1"><section numlevel="1" lineno="24" slineno="1-2" number="41-1a-1226" type="enact"><secline lineno="23">Section 1. Section <bold>41-1a-1226</bold> is enacted to read:</secline><catline lineno="24"><bold>41-1a-1226<parens/>. Heavy duty emissions compliance fee -- Deposit.</bold></catline><subsection ssid="7-17" dnum="_-o:1-i" numlevel="1" lineno="25" slineno="1-3" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1" placement="noreturn"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1000" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(1)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="75" groupid="58" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">As used in this section:</amend><subsection ssid="7-30" dnum="_-o:a-i" numlevel="1" lineno="26" slineno="1-4" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1001" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(a)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="84" groupid="65" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">"High emissions heavy duty vehicle" means a motor vehicle that has:</amend><subsection ssid="7-20" dnum="_-o:i-i" numlevel="1" lineno="27" slineno="1-5" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1002" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(i)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="87" groupid="67" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">a gross vehicle weight rating of more than 14,000 pounds; and</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="7-21" dnum="_-o:ii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="28" slineno="1-6" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1003" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(ii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="90" groupid="69" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">a model year of 2009 or older.</amend></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="7-22" dnum="_-o:b-i" numlevel="1" lineno="29" slineno="1-7" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="2"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1004" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(b)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="93" groupid="71" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">"High emissions heavy duty vehicle" does not include:</amend><subsection ssid="7-23" dnum="_-o:i-i" numlevel="1" lineno="30" slineno="1-8" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1005" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(i)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="96" groupid="73" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">a farm tractor;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="7-24" dnum="_-o:ii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="31" slineno="1-9" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1006" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(ii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="99" groupid="75" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">a farm truck;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="7-25" dnum="_-o:iii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="32" slineno="1-10" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1007" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(iii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="102" groupid="77" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">an implement of husbandry;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="7-26" dnum="_-o:iv-i" numlevel="1" lineno="33" slineno="1-11" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1008" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(iv)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="105" groupid="79" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">an ambulance;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="7-27" dnum="_-o:v-i" numlevel="1" lineno="34" slineno="1-12" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1009" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(v)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="108" groupid="81" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">a law enforcement vehicle;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="7-28" dnum="_-o:vi-i" numlevel="1" lineno="35" slineno="1-13" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1010" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(vi)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="111" groupid="83" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">a fire engine;</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="7-46" dnum="_-o:vii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="36" slineno="1-14" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1011" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(vii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="165" groupid="120" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">a vehicle owned and used by the United States government or by the state or a <ln numlevel="1" lineno="37" slineno="1-15"/>political subdivision of the state; or</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="7-49" dnum="_-o:viii-i" numlevel="1" lineno="38" slineno="1-16" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="3"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1012" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(viii)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="170" groupid="124" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">a vehicle designed and used for the collection and transportation of municipal <ln numlevel="1" lineno="39" slineno="1-17"/>solid waste and garbage.</amend></subsection></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="7-1" dnum="_-o:2-i" numlevel="1" lineno="40" slineno="1-18" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1013" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(2)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="29" groupid="21" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">Except as provided in Section <xref depth="3" refnumber="41-1a-1209">41-1a-1209</xref>, beginning on January 1, 2027, an applicant <ln numlevel="1" lineno="41" slineno="1-19"/>shall pay a heavy duty emissions compliance fee in an amount of $175 at the time an <ln numlevel="1" lineno="42" slineno="1-20"/>application is made for registration or renewal of a high emissions heavy duty vehicle.</amend></subsection><subsection ssid="7-12" dnum="_-o:3-i" numlevel="1" lineno="43" slineno="1-21" ea="amend" anum="0" owner="jchristopherson" style="1" level="1"><display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1014" style="1" owner="i" level="1" amendtag="start">(3)</amend></display><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="64" groupid="49" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="end">The division shall deposit revenue generated under Subsection <xref depth="4" refnumber="41-1a-1226(2)">(2)</xref> into the <ln numlevel="1" lineno="44" slineno="1-22"/>Transportation Fund created in Section 72-2-102.</amend></subsection></section></bsec><bsec buid="32" type="uncod" untype="effdate" src="uncod" uid="EF0000" sort="UZEFF" langlock="true" numlevel="1" lineno="45" slineno="2-1" sn="2"><section type="uncod" untype="effdate" display="false" src="uncod"><secline lineno="45">Section 2.  <bold>Effective Date.</bold></secline><sectionText lineno="46"><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="1" groupid="1" style="1" owner="jchristopherson" level="1" amendtag="both">This bill takes effect on <effdate uid="code" date="5/6/2026">May 6, 2026</effdate>.</amend></sectionText></section></bsec></bdy><foot><rev><tm>2-20-26 5:34 PM</tm></rev></foot></leg>